Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.06,0:52:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not alive anymore?\Nno
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.70,0:52:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,no?\Noh
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.35,0:52:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that\Nso success
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.69,0:52:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack Benny's not alive anymore?\Nno?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.53,0:52:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so success is\Nis
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.63,0:52:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is something that\Nwe all work for
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.41,0:52:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we do it with balance\Nand we achieve our goals
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.87,0:52:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,um\Ndoes God's will
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.29,0:52:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,have anything to do with that?\Nwell I think God's will is like the weather
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.74,0:53:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it influences everything\Nok
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.12,0:53:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,um both directly and indirectly\Num both directly and indirectly
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.08,0:53:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think God's will is that we as human beings fulfill our potentiality\Nand because the human spirit goes on from one physical lifetime on to another
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.69,0:53:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it grows over a number of physical lifetimes you know\Nand we call it karma
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.11,0:53:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it needs four or five physical lifetimes\Nto fulfill a spiritual goal
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.97,0:53:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\Nlike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.97,0:53:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\NI feel happy that we went to church
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.05,0:53:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel happy that we went to church\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.88,0:53:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this week\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.36,0:53:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that's an occasion that I\NI don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.36,0:53:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in previous years did we go for Ash Wednesday?\NI don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.36,0:53:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so\Ndid we?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.36,0:53:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\Noh ok
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.84,0:53:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,uh\Nwell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.99,0:54:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's both symbolic on a very deep level\Nand on another level it's not even necessary you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.09,0:54:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?\Nso I say to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.22,0:54:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,now why in the world do we get up early and go to Ash Wednesday?\Nto go to church today you see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.60,0:54:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\Nevery year the answer is different
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.88,0:54:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,right\Nuh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.88,0:54:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're in a different mood a different decade of life\Nand the older you get the more you realize that you better be going to church every Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.36,0:54:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\Nuh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.00,0:54:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the closer you get to being a hundred the more you know it's important you go to church every Sunday\Nuh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.00,0:54:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\Nuh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.19,0:54:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,do you feel like we've covered everything you want to say on success?\Noh well I could talk all day long about success
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.11,0:54:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know and as a psychiatrist I uh\Nthat often became important
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.42,0:55:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,whether when it's successful in their marriage as a father as a parent\Nin their children in their physical expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.46,0:55:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,financial self expectation is so important\Nuh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.16,0:55:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and so in defining success\NI hope as we speak today that I'm being as fluent
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.20,0:55:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as possible in fulfilling your questions\Nso that would be to me success
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.30,0:55:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then if on the way home from here I suddenly think I should have answered it better in a certain area\Nthen I will consider myself successful if I stopped feeling guilty that I didn't answer it better
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.86,0:55:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh\NI guess we're going to wrap it up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.12,0:55:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wrap it up, okay.\NSo is there anything else you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.99,0:56:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I feel myself to be successful that I have you in my life\Nand that the two of us are sitting here and the camera is focused on us
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.67,0:56:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore that more than just you and myself will be hearing this,\NI consider that the fulfillment of success,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.72,0:56:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that your life is contributing to the life of others.\NSo to me, success is your life is contributing to the life of others
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.20,0:56:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if nothing else but stirring up the question in their own mind\Nafter they listen to this and they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.31,0:56:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,well, what do I consider success?\NYeah, it brings up the question in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.35,0:56:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all grow through the questions that we ask ourselves.\NSo to the degree that we're helping other people to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.83,0:56:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel my life is a success.\NAnd I thank you for making my life a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.78,0:56:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you for being in mine.\NThank you, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.66,0:57:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.\NOkay.
